            <label for="question7"><b>7. What does your pokémon budget look like?</b></label>
            <div>
                <input type="radio" id="option1" name="question7" value="Option 1" required>
                <label for="option1">Pretty good, but I’d like to avoid any major expenses.</label>
            </div>
            <div>
